Package com.whirvis.jraknet.chat.client.frame

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChatBoxKeyListener
    Listens for presses to the enter button in the chat box.
    ChatFrame
    The frame used to visualize the ChatClient.
    ChatFrame.TextChannelRenderer
    The render used in place of the default so that the text channels list uses the actual name of the channel, rather than defaulting to it's TextChannel.toString() method.
    ComboBoxTextChannelListener
    Listens for changes in the currently selected channel.
    ConnectServerListener
    Used to listen for presses to the connect/disconnect button in the frame.
    UpdateUsernameBoxListener
    Used to listen for presses to the update username button in the frame.
